translated: Krasse, Nils Jerker, first assistant physician, Ljungby, born 14/2/14 in Malmö, to unmarried Nils K. and Hilda Eriksson. Married in 1938 to Harriette Hasselstad. Children: Ulfhild born in 1939, Görel in 1946. Received Medical License in 1944. Acting municipal physician in Klippan, acting chief city physician in Kalmar, and acting assistant physician at Blekinge's 1st sanatorium in Fur in 1944. Acting third assistant physician at the surgical clinic in Malmö in 1945. Assistant physician at the county hospital in Sveg from 1945 to 1946. Second assistant physician at the county hospital in Ljungby in 1946. First assistant physician there since 1947.
